{"header":{"word":"שְׁבִי","entry":9623,"letter":"שׂ","strongs":7628,"page":985},"definitions":[{"title":"Def","body":" &#134; [[שְׁבִי]] ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"n.m.","body":":1Sa 49:24 captivity, captives (coll.);&#8212;&#180;[[שׁ]]: abs. Ex 12:29 +, cstr. Ezr 2:1 +; [[שֶָׁבִי]] Nu 21:1 +; sf. [[שֶׁבְיְךָ]] Ju Jdg 5:12, [[שִׁבְיוֹ]] De 21:10, [[שְׁבִיכֶם]] Nu 31:19, etc.;&#8212;","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"1.","body":" = state of captivity, &#180;[[הָלַח בַּשְּׁ]]: Am 9:4, De 28:41, Na 3:10, Je 20:6, Je 22:22, Je 30:16, Ez Eze 12:11 (+ [[בַּגּוֹלָה]]) Eze 30:17, Eze 30:18, Is 46:2, La 1:18, = [[הָלַח שְׁבִי]] v:La 1:5 [[בַּשְּׁבִי יׇבִא]] Da 11:8; &#180;[[נׇתַן בַּשְּׁ]]: Ezr 9:7, &#180;[[נׇתַן לַשְּׁ]]: Ps 78:61, [[לֻקַּח בַּשֶָּׁבִי]] Je 48:46; [[וַאֲשֶׁר לַשְּׁבִי לַשֶָּׁבִי]] Je 15:2, Je 43:11, &#180;[[וְנׇשֵׁינוּ בַּשְּׁ]]: 2Ch 29:9 [[בִּשְׁבִי]] instr. of judgment Da 11:33; &#180;[[אֶרֶץ שׁ]]: Je 30:10, Je 46:27, 2Ch 6:37, 2Ch 6:38; phr. of deliverance (only Ezr Ne): &#180;[[נִשְׁאֲרוּ מִן־הַשְּׁ]]: Ne 1:2, cf .v:Ne 1:3, &#180;[[הַשָּׁבִים מִן־הַשְּׁ]]: Ne 8:17, [[הָעׂלִים מִשְּׁבִי הַגּוֹלָה]] Ezr 2:1 = Ne 7:6, &#180;[[הַבָּאִים מֵהַשְּׁ]]: Ezr 3:8, Ezr 8:35. ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"2.","body":" act of capture, [[סוּסֵיכֶם]] &#180;[[עִם שׁ]]: Am 4:10; [[שִׁמְלַת שִׁבְיׇהּ]] De 21:13 i. e. garb in which she was captured (&#62; others  captivity, in both: Am 4:10 = your captive horses; De 21:13  he captive&#8217;s garb). ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"3","body":" = captives (coll): Ex 12:29 (J), Nu 31:12, Nu 31:19, Nu 31:26 (man and beast), Is 20:4 (&#8214;[[גׇּלוּת ]] Is 49:24, Is 49:25, Hb Hab 1:9 + Ez Eze 32:9 LXX al. (v. [[שֶׁבֶר]] ad fin); appar. fs. Is 52:2 (but v. [[שָׁבִי]]); object of [[שָׁבָה]] (q.v.) Ju Jdg 5:12 (&#62; [[שׁׂבֶיךָ]] SyrVer JDMich We Bu Now), Nu 21:1 (JE), De 21:10, Ps 68:19, 2Ch 28:17.\r","content":"definition","show":"block"}],"notes":"","etymology":[],"morphology":[]}